      BASIS_SET DZVP-MOLOPT-SR-GTH
      POTENTIAL GTH-PBE
    &END KIND
    &KIND H_GHOST
      BASIS_SET DZVP-MOLOPT-SR-GTH
      GHOST
    &END KIND
 
